OL,3,CUniversity admits it 'could have done
OL,4,Cbetter' after student took own life
OL,6,FCardiff University has said it "could
OL,7,Fhave done better" after a student took
OL,8,Fher own life.
OL,10,FMared Foulkes, 21, from Anglesey, died
OL,11,Fin July 2020 - seven hours after
OL,12,Freceiving her results from Cardiff
OL,13,FUniversity.
OL,15,FThe results indicated that she had
OL,16,Ffailed one assessment and would not be
OL,17,Fable to continue into her third year,
OL,18,Fdespite the fact that she had re-sat
OL,19,Fher exam and passed.
