OL,6,FWendy Larner has been Vice Chancellor
OL,7,Fat Cardiff University since 2023.
OL,9,FShe added: "One of the things I did
OL,10,Fvery early on was to write to Mared's
OL,11,Ffamily and offer to meet with them.
OL,12,FThat offer remains open."
OL,14,FIn an interview with Wales this Week,
OL,15,FIona, Mared's mother said: "The
OL,16,Fpoliceman came here and said it was a
OL,17,Ffatal accident. And we just couldn't
OL,18,Fbelieve it - you think you're in a
OL,19,Fdream, you just can't believe what
OL,20,Fthey've said.
