OL,6,F"I just asked my husband to come
OL,7,Fthrough...and we have never been the
OL,8,Fsame again. This house has never been
OL,9,Fthe same again, this family unit has
OL,10,Fgone forever."
OL,12,FShe added that trying to get answers
OL,13,Ffrom the university about the
OL,14,Fcircumstances around Mared's death has
OL,15,Fbeen challenging.
OL,17,F"(It's been) long and difficult - very
OL,18,Ffrustrating, demeaning at times, and
OL,19,Fupsetting," she explained.
