OL,6,F"And you have to ask everything, it
OL,7,Fisn't forthcoming, you have to ask as
OL,8,Fparents."
OL,10,FWhen asked whether she felt Mared's
OL,11,Fdeath could have been prevented, Iona
OL,12,Fsaid: "Yes, definitely yes. It was a
OL,13,Fhuman error which should never have
OL,14,Fhappened.
OL,16,F"A tragedy like Mared's should not
OL,17,Fhave happened. Had she gone to a
OL,18,Fdifferent university, she would still
OL,19,Fbe with us. I am sure she would still
OL,20,Fbe with us."
