OL,3,CUniversity admits it 'could have done
OL,4,Cbetter' after student took own life
OL,6,FAt the inquest into Mared's death in
OL,7,FOctober 2021, the Coroner said the way
OL,8,FCardiff University communicated the
OL,9,Fresults was "complex and confusing".
OL,11,FWendy Larner said Cardiff University
OL,12,Fhas changed the way it gives results.
OL,14,FShe said: "A lot has changed and we
OL,15,Fhave learned from this very tragic
OL,16,Fevent. The students who receive their
OL,17,Fresults no longer have to wait until
OL,18,FSeptember for the outcome of resits,
OL,19,Fwhich was the case for Mared, and on
OL,20,Fthe transcripts the students get full
OL,21,Fresults of resits."
