OL,3,CUniversity admits it 'could have done
OL,4,Cbetter' after student took own life
OL,6,FCardiff University has also changed
OL,7,Fits processes in this area, according
OL,8,Fto Wendy Larner.
OL,10,FShe said: "All students provide a
OL,11,Freference for next of kin - what we
OL,12,Fnow ask them for is a trusted contact
OL,13,F- this is someone who the student
OL,14,Fthemself trusts, and importantly, we
OL,15,Fhave the opportunity, should we have
OL,16,Fserious concerns about the student, to
OL,17,Fgo to the trusted contact."
OL,19,FBut this would only happen with the
OL,20,Fstudent's permission.
